name: 米歇尔·丹纳
introduction: Michele Danna is an actress based in NYC. She will be playing the role of Sandra Maddox in the series Take The Whip (2023), and is performing Off-Broadway as Lady Macbeth.Michele is originally from New Jersey. Aside from her work on TV and film, she has extensive experience in theater. She is a director, coach, and writer. Michele attended Rider University and was a Governor's School of the Arts Acting Scholar.
